data.description: Discover the allure of this two-story townhome nestled in an exclusive gated community. Your journey begins through a private gated front patio, leading to an open main floor with a welcoming living room featuring a wet bar, raised hearth brick fireplace, and a sliding glass door which opens to the patio. The spacious kitchen offers a range stove, microwave hood vent, dishwasher, pantry, and ample cabinet and counter space. Enjoy meals in the bright dining room, adorned with a stylish chandelier. Luxuriate in brand-new vinyl plank flooring, plush carpeting, and fresh paint throughout. The main level also hosts a convenient half bath. The upper level unveils a spacious primary bedroom with a ceiling fan, walk-in closet, and private full bath. A well-appointed secondary bedroom with a private half bath, is separated by a hallway which includes a laundry closet. Descend to the lower level to discover a versatile bonus room and an attached two-car garage with direct access. Revel in the comfort of central air conditioning and heating, controlled by a Nest thermostat. The property features an intercom entry system, ensuring security. Enjoy proximity to Westfield Topanga, The Village, Northridge Fashion Center, Winnetka Park, schools, shops, and restaurants. Elevate your lifestyle with this secure and stylish townhome.
